  <Document>
    <name>Georgia Licensed Medical Cannabis Dispensaries</name>
    <description><![CDATA[The official map of licensed medical cannabis dispensaries in Georgia updated by the Georgia Access to Medical Cannabis Commission ("GMCC"). GMCC is the State of Georgia agency responsible for cannabis licensing, regulatory compliance, and providing access to patients on the Georgia Low THC Oil Patient Registry. <br><br>To verify the status of a license, or for more information about the patient registry, visit the Commission's website at www.gmcc.ga.gov]]></description>
